    "attributes": {
        "action": "Review Commercial leases, introduce a standard lease document & duty of care",
        "additional_details": "We think we need more retailers, but it could only happen if they are properly supported and risks limited. We think the government needs to implement duty of care as a responsibility for landlords as we feel they are reluctant to act upon changes of circumstances. We think introducing reasonable break clauses depending on circumstances could limit the losses.",
        "background": "Implement duty of care as a responsibility for landlords. Publish a standard formatted lease document which can be used by small businesses to help cut cost and time. Apart from standard breaks, introduce break clauses with reasonable notice based on circumstances.",
